{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01FADRi2tXSjZQbP15RJEQ8V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Build is green. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n**Harness: `h5_committed_type_fuzzer`**\n\nThe harness targets committed (named) datatype open and introspection:\n\n1. **File setup**: Writes fuzz input to a temp file and opens it read-only with `H5Fopen`.\n\n2. **Object traversal**: Uses `H5Ovisit3` to walk every object in the file hierarchy. For each `H5O_TYPE_NAMED_DATATYPE` object found, it calls `H5Topen2(file_id, name, H5P_DEFAULT)` — exactly as a real application would.\n\n3. **Deep introspection** via `introspect_type()` (depth-limited to 8 to avoid stack exhaustion):\n   - `H5Tget_class` + `H5Tget_size` — always called for any type\n   - **COMPOUND**: `H5Tget_nmembers`, per-member `H5Tget_member_name` (freed via `H5free_memory`), `H5Tget_member_offset`, `H5Tget_member_type` (recursed then closed)\n   - **ENUM**: `H5Tget_nmembers`, member names, `H5Tget_member_value`, base type via `H5Tget_super` (recursed)\n   - **VLEN**: `H5Tis_variable_str`, base type via `H5Tget_super` (recursed)\n   - **ARRAY**: `H5Tget_array_ndims`, `H5Tget_array_dims2`, element type via `H5Tget_super` (recursed)\n   - **STRING**: `H5Tis_variable_str`\n\n4. **Correct resource management**: every type handle from `H5Tget_member_type`/`H5Tget_super` is closed with `H5Tclose`; all `H5Tget_member_name` results freed with `H5free_memory`.\n\nThe seed corpus is seeded from HDF5's own test `.h5` files, many of which contain committed types."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":338,"cache_read_input_tokens":89028,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":338,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e09d83d7-89d6-46e2-